HELM  ?
  single user can serve docker container
  if million user ?cant serve so K8S -K8s cluster wil autoscale ,auto deploy,LB [lot of commd ]
  Managing k8s is big task  -so Helm chart (top of the  k8s) 
      helm chart provides top layer abstract with  minimal command  that internaly communicate with k8s
  comands:
    helm install my-app ./my-app
    helm uninstall my-app

pre-req-instal:
  -K8S cluster (eks,microk8s...) 
  -kubectl
  -configure .kube 
  and Helm chart

demo:
-->heml create helloworld
    //charts.yaml,values.yaml,templates   
